title: Metal Gear Solid (Almost Complete Soundtrack) OST
description:
Almost complete soundtrack, missing only these three releases: MGSV Phantom Pain
MGS Acid 2 and Ground Zeroes, maybe others but i don't know for sure.
What we have here? Well we have same songs, but not duplicated songs, they're different in quality that i guarantee, there is some rare songs in this compilation, but i know i should have added the missing ones, anyway this a compilation from various torrent and downloads, i never owned none of these songs in my life physically, never, so there aren't my work, i only redistribute files
